metadata.name: Go ahead, take it. It will be our secret
metadata.description:
Young Anuszka was left behind, collecting firewood and helping her father. When they got home, she was wearing a strange golden medallion. It was worth more than all their possessions. Nobody saw where she got it, who gave it to her or what it meant. No one except the dog.

Dark fairy godmother... few years later

Digital painting (2019)
